{"tid":2290821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟：關注民主派前立法會議員被捕","createTime":"2020-11-18T09:53:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-18T10:14:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0279a34cbb8a63a63619feeeef1cfd32b39aa3b9","tid":2290821,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T09:53:37.000Z","msg":"歐盟駐港澳辦事處關注民主派前立法會議員被捕<br />\n<br />\n歐盟駐港澳辦事處表示，密切跟進並關注民主派前立法會議員因立法會內發生的事件而被捕。<br />\n<br />\n3名立法會前議員包括許智峯、陳志全及朱凱廸分別被警方上門拘捕，指他們與早前立法會內潑臭水的事件有關，涉嫌違反《立法會（權力及特權）條例》及《侵害人身罪條例》，3人獲准保釋，案件明天在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560667-20201118.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560667-20201118.htm&d=KoeRi8LHiva86SpHjnbz1YleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=538630ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560667-20201118.htm&h=b310d3a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560667-20201118.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fbeff0b6658cdc48a57d633cf78b6bb57e3b4c5c","tid":2290821,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"拜登呢方面會唔會同歐盟一致呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ad7230157f8a7cd625b6edec187415ab33c57e","tid":2290821,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:05:09.000Z","msg":"關閪咩，禁撚多嗲，係就整個移民plan畀香港人啦，唔係就靜啦，繼續收屎色恐怖分子收飽佢冇人會話你㗎喎"},{"pid":"b0cd1bc1c02f5668802e5fcf333bfad56a8d19df","tid":2290821,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fbeff0b6658cdc48a57d633cf78b6bb57e3b4c5c","tid":2290821,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"拜登呢方面會唔會同歐盟一致呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:07:08.000Z","msg":"登登：一直持續關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b4550987377ac8da6f93ef545c5bcdb0ce256a","tid":2290821,"uid":193077,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"又關注"},{"pid":"5198a3ec9fed0ef9dab9440d65c5299e14a73aef","tid":2290821,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T10:14:15.000Z","msg":"關注完未？做嘢未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}